    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she still runs like a dream! It\u2019s been well-cared for and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a comfortable, dependable drive without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got plenty of heart and is just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
