    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is this E46-generation BMW M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. Under the hood lies the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual transmission paired with a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanical integrity has been prioritized: the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal phase timing. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive. Ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
