    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances executive luxury with everyday reliability. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Deep Charcoal Metallic that retains a high-gloss, mirror-like finish. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel, the body remains remarkably straight and free of any significant dents. Step inside to a pristine, smoke-free cabin featuring premium black leather upholstery. The seats are firm and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the walnut wood trim remains crack-free. All onboard technology, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service history. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. It has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection and is fitted with high-performance tires that have significant tread life remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
